name: CONCH
description: Conch Smart Chain (CSC) is the first product launched by the Conch Open Platform under the Conch Blockchain Research Institute. Conch Smart Chain is a decentralized, high-efficiency and energy-saving public chain that can realize the compatibility of smart contracts on the basis of supporting high-performance transactions. However, the goal of Conch Smart Chain is not only to be a public chain. Relying on the global transaction ecology, Conch Smart Chain is committed to becoming the birthplace of innovative technologies and innovative businesses, and building a complete ecosystem that integrates technology development, application promotion, and transactions. closed loop.
